title: A new airport added to Columbia in MSFS: Alberto Lleras Camargo Airport
description:
A new airport has been added to Columbia in MSFS: Alberto Lleras Camargo Airport (SKSO). The cool thing about this airport is that the elevation is pretty high: 6 KM in between two mountains which make flying to the approach to this airport very special.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
